DESIGN PRINCIPLES

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Segmentation by trust level
Default deny between VLANs
Centralized control via pfSense
Servers isolated from clients
IoT treated as untrusted
Sandbox treated as hostile
SUMMARY

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

This topology represents a segmented homelab architecture with:

Dedicated firewall (pfSense)
VLAN-based network segmentation
Separate server, client, and IoT networks
Centralized logging and identity services
Isolated sandbox environment (planned)

This is the current build-state topology and will evolve as connectivity and firewall policies are finalized.
